gle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 14, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wvb1665702780266.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wvb1665702780266.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wvb1665702780266.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wvb1665702780266\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Edit the Properties of\n      Multiple Objects</h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the Property Inspector to set a property on multiple subobjects to the same value.\n      This can be useful, for example, if you want to have several fields use the same data type or\n      same widget type.</p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__li_d1628e1_d1629e1_d1630e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__p_d4136e1_d4137e1_d4138e1\">Select multiple objects in the worksheet editor. You\n               can use Ctrl + click to select individual objects, or Shift + click to select the\n               first and last object in a range of objects.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__p_d4139e1_d4140e1_d4141e1\">Although it is possible to select objects of the\n                  different types, they have different properties, so there are few properties that\n                  could be usefully changed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__p_d4142e1_d4143e1_d4144e1\">Only properties that are shared by all the selected\n                  objects are displayed. Properties that have different values show the value\n                  (DIFFER) </p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__fig_d4145e1_d4146e1_d4147e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Properties Inspector with multiple fields selected</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Properties Inspector with multiple objects selected\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/pi_multipleobjects.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__li_d1631e1_d1632e1_d1633e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__p_d4151e1_d4152e1_d4153e1\">Change the value of the desired property. For\n               example, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">DSP Widget Type</span>. The change is applied to all\n               selected objects.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"wvb1665702780266__note_w320ab1b5b1b3b3b1_w321ab1b5b1b3b3_w322ab1b5b1b3_w323ab1b5b1_w324ab1b5_w325ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> It is not possible to change the value of the\n                     <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Name</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Full Name</span>,\n                     <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Location</span>, or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherits From</span>\n                  properties.</div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Edit the Properties of Multiple Objects Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 14, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Edit the Properties of Multiple Objects Use the Property Inspector to set a property on multiple subobjects to the same value. This can be useful, for example, if you want to have several fields use the same data type or same widget type. Select multiple objects in the worksheet editor. You can use Ctrl + click to select individual objects, or Shift + click to select the first and last object in a range of objects. Although it is possible to select objects of the different types, they have different properties, so there are few properties that could be usefully changed. Only properties that are shared by all the selected objects are displayed. Properties that have different values show the value (DIFFER) Figure 1. Properties Inspector with multiple fields selected Change the value of the desired property. For example, the DSP Widget Type . The change is applied to all selected objects. Note: It is not possible to change the value of the Name , Full Name , Location , or Inherits From properties. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}